items.directions: 1. Never cook ravioli in rapidly boiling water. 2. Always bring water to a boil first. 3. Lower heat and gently add frozen ravioli. 4. Low boil for 8 minutes, stirring occasionally, until they are pillowy. 5. Do not overcook! 6. Skim from water with a strainer spoon. Do not use a colander. 7. Gently toss with olive oil or Rising Moon pasta sauce. Keep frozen.

items.details: All natural. Build-your-own meal. Our balanced meal kit includes honey wheat crackers, grape jelly, creamy peanut butter and strawberry 100% fruit snacks. No artificial anything! 6 grams of protein. 7 g rams of whole grains. 1 serving of fruit. Real food for all. Crunchy honey wheat crackers. Sweet & simple all natural grape jelly. Squeezable all natural creamy peanut butter. Strawberry peel-apart 100% fruit snack. A balanced meal perfect for: lunchbox; on-the-go energy boost; after-school snack; at-work recharge. Real Food for All: At Revolution Foods we believe in foods that are whole. Foods made with carefully considered ingredients. And nutrient-rich foods that promote healthy growth and development. After all, creating smart minds starts with fueling healthy bodies. Ingredients shouldn't be six syllables long. And there shouldn't be 42 ingredients in a flavor. Our meal kits are all natural. Nothing fake. Nothing artificial. Because you deserve nothing less. To learn more, visit revolutionfoods.com. School of Thought: We're on a mission to transform the way America eats. Our story began in schools with two moms serving healthy, hand-prepared lunches to students. Today we serve over a million delicious meals a week to schools across the country. Now we're bringing our recipe for success in schools to your home. Thank you! - Kristin & Kirsten, Founding Mothers. Mom-approved. Wondering where our sugar comes from? 100% Fruit Snack: 13 g. All Natural Grape Jelly: 14 g. All Natural Peanut Butter: 2 g. See anything you don't recognize? Contact us to learn more. Share a story of healthy change you've made in your life! Carton made from 100% recycled fiber content, minimum 65% post-consumer material. Please recycle.
